headline: Agoda reveals: Shanghai is Asia's top emerging destination
summary: Shanghai has emerged as the fastest growing destination for attracting international travelers from Asia, according to digital travel platform Agoda. The Chinese metropolis is followed by Jeju (South Korea), Paris (France), Nha Trang (Vietnam), and Fukuoka (Japan).
